		"description": {
			"value": "<p>When you hit a creature with a weapon attack, you can expend a spell slot to deal &amp;reference[psychic] damage and attempt to frighten the target, in addition to the weapon's damage.</p><p><strong>[[/save wis]]{Wisdom Save}</strong> </p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 4d6 psychic]] damage* and is &amp;reference[frightened].</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> [[/damage 4d6 psychic]] damage, no other effect.*</p></li></ul><p><strong>*Using Higher Level Spell Slots:</strong> Damage increases by [[/r 1d6]] for each spell level above 3rd.</p>",
